            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-xs-center">

                <h3 class="mbr-section-title display-2">
                    Association <br>
                    « Nos Amis les Oiseaux » <br>
                    (NAO)
                    <p></p>
                </h3>

                <div class="lead">
                    <span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 1.07rem; line-height: 1.5;">
